    "desc": "phase 1: is revamp of look and feel\nphase 2: is to \"digitise\" in terms of going paperless for some users (and how this works in terms of opting in for this on frontend and backend)\nphase 3: digitise in terms of taking those steps and implementing on app\nphase 4: further digitising on app, adding in",
    "notionUrl": "https://www.notion.so/Recipe-Card-Revamp-1c0d973d4be346b0ae200884eb358dca",
    "priority": "P3",
