    "e": 1,
    "desc": "There is a data gap in the reporting for pause reasons on a week-to-week basis. The NPD team have proposed that we add a preventative measure to block users from closing the pause reason modal before providing a reason. We have taken on this project to look at wholistic ways of addressing the data g",
