        "text": "24 Jul\nScheduled for 18-19 Aug (due to schedules)\nMarketing to check and approve copy for invite and Form DONE\nCS to send out form DONE\nNPD to collect feedback and plan out each session\n(key stakeholders to use friends that are “of our target market” to fill in gaps in tastings” if need be) \nIncentive to customers to join us for the tasting - freebies from WH and 25% of frozen meals - form NPD budget\n\nDeon to start finalising plan and next steps for Timeline (to be completed by end of next week (4th) for review and tweaks)"
