        "author": "Product Workspace",
        "date": "2023-02-16T09:32:00.000Z",
        "text": "@Anonymous - Thanks so much for the work and effort into making this product card! Think it looks great! 🙂 Happy with the isle page/product preview.  I see on the PDP that there are 2 options shown with the position of the serving size - option 1 being below the price and option 2 being between the price and description. Please can we go with the serving size being stated below the price (i.e. option 1) - Think the word flow/structure is nicer that way. Also happy with the set up of the nutri info😊"
