        "date": "2023-03-06T07:45:00.000Z",
        "text": "@Anonymous yes that is completely configurable your side. Please do so on the staging site and let me know if you are then happy with the way the sub title and description pull through on the PDP. If not, we can make changes so just let me know 🙂"
