        "author": "Product Workspace",
        "date": "2024-08-22T08:10:00.000Z",
        "text": "@Willow Davey as discussed happy for you to run with this one.\n\nHigh-level Considerations\nBack End\n1. FTN Collect method needs to be ported across to FTN\n2. Carrier Rates sheet will need to be modified (assuming that we will use a similar rule to the one FTN has set up)\n\nFront End\n1. Email templates might need to be modified\n2. Order States and statuses may need to be modified\n3. Account pages will need to be reviewed \n    - Order History \n    - Latest Order Pages"
