        "date": "2023-08-15T13:36:00.000Z",
        "text": "Update 15/08\nAll physical conversions complete - weighed and tested. @Anonymous to apply conversions to the rest of ingredients that need to change. The ready to pull the trigger. \n\nNext steps:\n@Anonymous to confirm all ingredient conversions\n@Anonymous @Anonymous @Anonymousto test on staging."
