        "date": "2024-01-26T06:21:00.000Z",
        "text": "12 Jan\nNot expecting any massive Margin reductions in FY25 - rather further cost savings to mitigate price increases\n\nMajor projects for FY25 to ultimately reduce margin:\n- Boxes (Future and WRB and Kalideck TBC) - potential decrease but TBC; Kalideck trial completed - report here\n- Soft plastics potential price decrease if increasing Future pack basket size and some negotiation\n- Usage reductions \n- Issuing to track usage (and SC on Acu)\n- Understanding returns and reusability"
