        "date": "2023-03-28T09:03:00.000Z",
        "text": "@Natalie Thayer @Gershom Rademeyer please have a look at the insights ive provided here. If you feel that these insights will meet the proposed requirement. I am more than happy to set this up on staging for us to test and use as a basis for all further discussions.\n\nIf we do go ahead with the proposed idea I do think its worth while crunching some numbers to see what the effects could look like (specifically in relation to discount budget). \nie. we could have @Anonymous run numbers on all existing customers that have between 2 and 3 MK orders to see how big a spend we might be opening ourselves up to (excluding any actual acquisition numbers)"
