        "date": "2023-04-14T07:49:00.000Z",
        "text": "@Anonymous Lets try and set up examples of everything listed in the table on staging A. \n@Natalie Thayer one thing I think is absolutely critical is a written list of considerations, concerns and current limitations. This way we can all keep each other and the greater business honest (might even be worthwhile having this in place for general discounts). I’ll start a draft of this and lets see where we end up.\n\ncc @Sahil @Gershom Rademeyer"
